description:
Bang Your Head - how fast is your head? 


Head speed is important in concert - in our little game, the correct question relates to finger speed. 

TamsPalm proudly presents Bang Your Head, which brings the headbanging experience on the road. Use your keyboard to move the figures head and show the world who is the master. 

Sounds interesting? Then what about banging to your favorite metal/rock songs? Yes you heard right. You're able to add songs of your media library.    

Note that this is just a little game, a simple fun-app. Please don't give a bad rating just because you don't see the fun in it. If you like the app: download the full version to support it. Here's a free test version and you're never forced to download the full version...
